Symbol.Script_3D:
! Work Sink
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
res = 24 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN res = 8 ! Simple
IF useSysMat THEN MainBoxMaterial = sMat MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL res
! --- WORK SINK --- !
unID = 1 HOTSPOT 0, 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, B, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, B, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, 0, -ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, 0, -ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, B, -ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, B, -ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN ! Detailed ADDz -ZZYZX+edgeThick PRISM_ 10,ZZYZX-edgeThick, 0,0, 14, 0,B, 14, A,B,14, A,0,14, 0,0, -1, edgeThick, edgeThick, 15, edgeThick, B-edgeThick, 15, A-edgeThick,B-edgeThick,15, A-edgeThick,edgeThick,15, edgeThick, edgeThick, -1 DEL 1
CUTPOLYA 2,1,0, ConPosX_3,ConPosY_3,915, ConWidth_3/2,360,4015
ADDz -ZZYZX PRISM_ 4,edgeThick, 0,0, 11, 0,B, 11, A,B,11, A,0,11 DEL 1
CUTEND
ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN ! Simple ADDz -ZZYZX EXTRUDE 4,0,0,ZZYZX, 1+4+16+32, 0,0, 0, 0,B, 0, A,B,0, A,0,0 DEL 1 ENDIF
ADD (ConPosX_1 + ConPosX_2)/2, (ConPosY_1 + ConPosY_2)/2, (ConPosZ_1 + ConPosZ_2)/2 GOSUB 1000 DEL 1
DEL TOP RESOL res
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, cShow3D = 1, gs_ConMat = MainBoxMaterial, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 16, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConPosZ_2=ConPosZ_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 16, ConPosX_3=ConPosX_3, ConPosY_3=ConPosY_3, ConPosZ_3=ConPosZ_3, ConLength_3=ConLength_3, ConEdit_3 = 15
END
1000: ! Tap
tx = ABS(ConPosX_1 - ConPosX_2)/2 bx = 0.006 by = 0.030
FOR i=1 TO 2 ADDx -tx ROTx 90 CYLIND 0.05,0.015 ADDz 0.02 IF tx > 0.015+EPS THEN ARMC 0.015, 0.015, tx, 0,0,90 ENDIF ADDz 0.035 ROTz i*15 PRISM 12,0.007, -bx, bx, -bx, by, bx, by, bx, bx, by, bx, by,-bx, bx,-bx, bx,-by, -bx,-by, -bx,-bx, -by,-bx, -by, bx DEL 5
MULX -1 NEXT i DEL 2
ADDy -0.02 ROTy -90 ARMC 0.015, 0.015, 0.02, 0,0,90 DEL 1 ROTx 90 ROTy -90 ADDz -0.01 PRISM_ 10,0.02, 0.147986393591, 0.09234439178515, 15, 0.04117544321573, 0.09234439178515, 79, -0.01198261107796, 0.04424275934702, 79, -0.01198261107796, 0.02, 15, 0.01198261107796, 0.02, 15, 0.01198261107796, 0.04424275934702, 79, 0.04737063515823, 0.07626465611579, 79, 0.127986393591, 0.07626465611579, 15, 0.127986393591, 0.05893770166193, 15, 0.147986393591, 0.05893770166193, 15 DEL 4
RETURN
Symbol.Script_2D:
! Work Sink
PEN gs_cont_pen SET FILL gs_fill_type
unID = 1 DrawingNum = 1 IF DrawingNum = 1 THEN ! Top
! --- WORK SINK --- !
HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, B, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A, B, unID: unID=unID+1
IF GLOB_CONTEXT <> 22 THEN POLY2_B 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0,0, 1, 0,B, 1, A,B,1, A,0,1 POLY2_B 4, 1+4, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, edgeThick, edgeThick, 1, edgeThick, B-edgeThick, 1, A-edgeThick,B-edgeThick,1, A-edgeThick,edgeThick,1
CIRCLE2 ConPosX_3,ConPosY_3, ConWidth_3/2 ENDIF ENDIF DEL TOP
! --- OTHER VIEWS --- !
ROT2 (SYMB_MIRRORED - NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED)) * (DrawingNum > 1) * SYMB_ROTANGLE
IF DrawingNum = 2 THEN PROJECT2 -3, 90, 2 ! Bottom IF DrawingNum = 3 THEN PROJECT2 4, 270, 2 ! Front IF DrawingNum = 4 THEN PROJECT2 4, 90, 2 ! Back IF DrawingNum = 5 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180 * SYMB_MIRRORED, 2 ! Right IF DrawingNum = 6 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180 * NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Left
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, DrawingNum = DrawingNum, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type=gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen=gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen=gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 15, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 15, ConPosX_3=ConPosX_3, ConPosY_3=ConPosY_3, ConLength_3=ConLength_3, ConEdit_3 = 5 DEL 1
END
